# ============================================================================
# Configuration Guide
# ============================================================================
#
# Chip Allocation:
# - chips: [0]           → Single chip (fastest startup)
# - chips: [0, 1]        → Tensor parallel (better quality)
# - chips: [0, 1, 2, 3]  → 4-chip parallel (best quality)
#
# Sharing Endpoints:
# - Multiple tasks can share same URL (sequential requests)
# - Good for cost savings when not all tasks run simultaneously
#
# Endpoint Types:
# - type: text (default)      → Text completion API
# - type: image               → Image generation API
# - type: embedding           → Embedding API
#
# Temperature Guide:
# - 0.0-0.2  → Deterministic (translation, facts)
# - 0.3-0.7  → Balanced (strategy, decisions)
# - 0.8-1.2  → Creative (art, storytelling)
#
# Max Tokens Guide:
# - 200-300  → Short responses (commands)
# - 500-600  → Medium (with thinking)
# - 800-1000 → Long (complex reasoning, art)
#
# ============================================================================
